data.description: CHEAP ELECTRIC BILLS!   SOLAR PANELS INCLUDED W/SALE!   SPECTACULAR GOLF COURSE VIEW FROM THIS CUSTOM BUILT HOUSE - 2BD/2BA ON GOLF COURSE!  NEW ROOF with over $30,000 worth of solar panels installed, which are  INCLUDED in the sale.  There is an existing transferable Warranty.   Lush landscaping leads to this newly painted exterior of house (2022) .  This house greets with a double door entrance into the large living room that overlooks the Florida room.  The house has a formal dining room with plenty of room for a table, chairs and China closet.   The kitchen has  a clear top range, refrigerator, built in dishwasher, time saving microwave with plenty of storage and a center island for great  organization.  The sitting area is directly off the kitchen for enjoying many dinners.  There is an office next to the sitting area that has a wonderful view of the golf course.  This house has a split bedroom plan.  The Master bedroom is large enough to accommodate a king size bed and ample furniture.  The Master bathroom has a double sink vanity with storage, soaking tub, walk in shower and a walk in closet.  The guest bathroom has a walk-in shower, linen closet and plenty of storage.  The Florida room has a great view of the golf course which has an outstanding view.   Furniture for sale. .  IDEAL LOCATIONS: : Close to Clubhouse, Tennis Courts, Outdoor Olympic Size Pool, Indoor Heated Pool, Tennis, Bocce and Shuffleboard Courts, Library, Ping-Pong, Craft, Pool Table, Exercise Room and much more. GREAT LOCATION: Close to Shopping Across the Street at Publix, Walgreens Various Banks, Restaurants, Liquor Store, Gold's Gym , etc. 1 1/2 miles East of the World Equestrian Center. 1 1/2 Hours from Orlando and all the Attractions including Disney World, Universal Studios, Lego Land, Sea World, Epcot, the Airport, etc. 1 1/2 Hours from Both Coasts. All measurements are approximate. Buyer(s) to re-measure.
